a photograph of her

6
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:19,375
from Commander Karasuma.

7
00:00:19,458 --> 00:00:21,375
[MAEHARA]
Whoa! She's perfect!

8
00:00:21,458 --> 00:00:23,583
