73
00:03:33,666 --> 00:03:35,250
[KORO-SENSEI]
Okie-dokie, boys n' girls!

74
00:03:35,333 --> 00:03:37,833
This will be your first quest
with our new party member!

75
00:03:37,916 --> 00:03:40,083
I expect every one
of you to level up!

76
00:03:40,166 --> 00:03:42,333
[CLASS]
Yes, sir!

77
00:03:42,416 --> 00:03:44,625
