nothin' this guy can't do.

209
00:08:52,583 --> 00:08:53,625
[KORO-SENSEI]
Moral of the story:

210
00:08:53,708 --> 00:08:55,708
A good hero is a
jack of all trades.

211
00:08:55,791 --> 00:08:58,458
So be sure not to neglect
your ancient language studies!

212
00:08:58,541 --> 00:08:59,250
[CLASS]
Yes, sir!

213
00:08:59,333 --> 00:09:00,458
[KORO-SENSEI]
ZIp!

214
00:09:00,541 --> 00:09:02,166
Now, uh, getting back
to our little spell

215
00:09:02,250 --> 00:09:04,125
for banishing pixilation
we talked about earlier.

216
00:09:04,208 --> 00:09:06,416
That's not what she's for!

